content: I'm trying to optimize my daily commute. I've been taking the 7:15 am train from Oakdale station to downtown every weekday for a while now. I've noticed it's always crowded on Mondays and Fridays. Do you have any suggestions to avoid the crowds or make my commute more efficient? By the way, I spend around $12.50 per day on train tickets and coffee, so any tips on reducing that expense would be great too.
